1)includes static factory methods for List,Set and Map interface

2)Userfull for creating small number of collection

var list = new ArrayList<>();

list.add("SPRING BOOT");

list.add("microservices"); list.add("DOCKER");

===>SIMPLIFIES========>

List<String> list  =list.of("Spring boot","microservices","docker");

list.stream().forEach(System.out::println);
